instance horizontal_integration : DTDFVocab:HoriIntegration [
    base:desc "Inter‑entity communication uses ROS2 as the primary data‑exchange mechanism. For integration with external systems, the design references ISO 23247, which permits the use of standards such as OPC Unified Architecture (OPC UA); thus the DTS can interoperate with enterprise systems or other digital twins via OPC UA gateways, although the current implementation relies on ROS2 communication."
